# HTTPS Requirements

## Production HTTPS Requirements
- All production deployments MUST use HTTPS
- Spotify OAuth requires HTTPS for redirect URIs in production
- Use HTTP only for local development (localhost)
- Update SPOTIFY_REDIRECT_URI to use https:// in production
- Ensure SSL certificates are properly configured

## Development vs Production
- Local development: HTTP allowed (localhost)
- Production deployment: HTTPS mandatory
- SSL certificates must be valid and properly configured
- CORS must be configured for production domain